  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1068210/extras/5e52e910cb33aefa1c1b8883a54d81e5.poster.avif?t=1585064468\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1068210/extras/5e52e910cb33aefa1c1b8883a54d81e5.webm?t=1585064468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1068210/extras/5e52e910cb33aefa1c1b8883a54d81e5.mp4?t=1585064468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Maze VR</h2>You can play The Maze VR with up to 8 people.<br>Race, Punch, Grab, Shoot and Think your way through each challenge.<br>If you solve the VR Room you can choose one of the doors to progress further into The Maze<br>and find your teamplayers to unlock the Big Master Multiplayer Room.<br><br>Share knowledge about the rooms and try to get the best The Maze time ever!<br><br>We now support LIV! We are curious about the great video's you'll produce with this amazing feature :)",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1068210/extras/5e52e910cb33aefa1c1b8883a54d81e5.poster.avif?t=1585064468\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1068210/extras/5e52e910cb33aefa1c1b8883a54d81e5.webm?t=1585064468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1068210/extras/5e52e910cb33aefa1c1b8883a54d81e5.mp4?t=1585064468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Maze VR</h2>You can play The Maze VR with up to 8 people.<br>Race, Punch, Grab, Shoot and Think your way through each challenge.<br>If you solve the VR Room you can choose one of the doors to progress further into The Maze<br>and find your teamplayers to unlock the Big Master Multiplayer Room.<br><br>Share knowledge about the rooms and try to get the best The Maze time ever!<br><br>We now support LIV! We are curious about the great video's you'll produce with this amazing feature :)",
